K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-11: sems bskyed pa tsam nyid na rang 'byung ngo //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-12: lus la gos bgos pa rnams ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-13: kha dog rnam pa sna tshogs par bcos pa /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-14: rnam pa sna tshogs par dri dang ldan pa'i ma
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-15: btags pa'i tshad mchog dang ldan pa de dag rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-16: kyis lha sred pa dang bcas pa rnams ngoms par
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-17: mi 'gyur ro // gzhan yang lha rnams yid kyis
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-18: don 'di dag dpyod par byad pa na de dang
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-19: de rang gi las dang 'dra bar phun sum tshogs
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-20: mi 'gyur ro // par 'gyur te / mchog tu
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-21: dga' bas ji ltar zas dang btung ba'i sa rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-22: la song nas lha bdud rtsi za bar byed do
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-23: mi 'gyur ro // par 'gyur te / // de dag gis zos pa de dag rnams ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:171b-24: sbyin pa rnams dang 'dra bar dman pa dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-2: lha rnams kyang rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i btung ba
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-3: dag 'thung par byed pa de dag rnams kyang dman
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-4: pa dang / bar ma'i ltung ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-6: rang gi las kyi rgyu'i rjes dang 'dra ba'i phyir ro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-7: ji ltar gang dag gis lus kyi tshad kyi rnam
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-8: pa ji srid du 'gyur ba'i rnam pa de srid
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-9: kho nar skyes bu de'i grib ma nyi ma rang
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-10: bzhin du gnas pa na 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-11: de kho na bzhin du lha rnams kyi yang gang
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-12: gis ji srid kyi rnam pa'i las rnams byas par
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-13: 'gyur ba de dag gi rnam pa de srid kho
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-14: na'i zas kyi rigs rnams skye'o //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-15: de za bar byed pa na'ang lha de dag rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-16: tshogs pa na za bar byed pas de dag mchog
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-18: de la lha rnams rgyu ba'i dus su nye bar
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-19: gnas pa rnams shin tu rgya che ba'i sdug bsngal
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-20: chen po dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-21: khyad par du'ang lha mo'i tshogs kyi mdun du ngo
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-22: tsha bar gyur pa'i sdug bsngal gyi mchog de 'dra
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-23: ba ni / srid pa gzhan na cung zad kyang med do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-24: slu ba med pa po'i bde bar gyur pa'i de
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-25: ltar so sor bstan pa de dag rnams kyis kyang
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172a-26: ji ltar gzhan du'ang 'khor ba thams cad du des
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-1: gzhan yang lha rnams kyi tha ma'i dus legs par
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-2: byas pa zad nas 'chi po ba'i dus na sdug
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-4: gang gi che bag med par spyod pa'i lha rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-5: rtag tu 'dod pa la rnam par chags pa las
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-7: 'chi 'pho ba de'i cha'ang 'dod pa sdug pa yid
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-8: du 'ong bar gyur pa gang dag rnams dang bral
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-10: snum zad pa'i dbang gis mar me bzhin du 'gag
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-11: par gyur pa na 'gro ba gzhan gang yin pa
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-12: dang 'dra ba'i rtags rnams sngon byung bar gyur pa
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-13: dang / 'chi 'pho ba'i dus kyi sdug bsngal de
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-14: dag rnams kyis lus dang yid mngon par bcom par
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-15: gyur pa'i rnams la sdug bsngal gang dag skye bar
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-17: dper brjod par sla ba yang ma yin no; ;de
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-18: nas de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das kyis tshigs su bcad
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-20: sna tshogs bde dang bag med dang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-21: yul rnams kyis kyang bslus pas kyang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-22: tshe zad 'chi ba'i dus su ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-23: lhan cig gnas pa yod ma yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-24: sngon chad bag med spyad pa yis //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-25: sbyin la sogs la mi 'jug go /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-26: phyi nas 'chi ba'i dus na de //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-27: rang gi sems ni sreg pa yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:172b-28: dang po bar dang de bzhin mthar //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-1: pa'i yid ni bya ba yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-2: legs par spyod dang rtag tu dul //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-3: 'chi ba'i dus na zhum pa med //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-5: sdug pa dang yang bral ba yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-6: yul rnams kyis ni rab bcom pas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-7: byis pa rnams ni spyod pa'ang med //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-8: de ni rim gyis rtogs 'gyur gyi //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-9: 'di ni khong du chung pa min //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-10: yul gyis rnam par nyams pa'i lha //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-11: 'dod pa la ni rnam zhen blo //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-12: 'dus bral sdug bsngal gang skyes pa'i //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-13: lha gang gang du skye ba yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-14: yud tsam gcig kyang de dag la //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-15: blo ni gnas par mi bya'o //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-16: mi rtag pa dang 'jigs dang bcas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-17: 'dod pas rtag tu 'khol byed po; ;de lta na yang rmongs pas byis //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-18: phyir zhing de nyid sten par byed //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-19: 'dod chags me yis rtag tu sreg /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-20: lha ni rnam par rmongs pa yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-21: bsregs par gyur nas phyis kyang de //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-22: yang dang yang du bsngags par byed //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-23: yul rnams la ni chags med par //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-24: rgyu gang de nyid la gzhol pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-25: gang yang de ni rab bsngags pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-26: de dag sdug bsngal rtag par gnas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-27: khams gsum 'di dag thams cad ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173a-28: zo chun khor mo bzhin du 'khor //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-0: las kyi zhags @173b pas kun bzung yang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-1: de nyid mthong ba yang ma yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-2: skye ba dang ni 'chi ba rnams //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-3: skye dang skye bar yang yang ngo //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-4: sems can rnam par rmongs dga' ba //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-5: rtag tu sdug bsngal skal ldan yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-6: glog dang zo chun 'khor lo dang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-7: mtshungs par 'dod pa rab tu bsgrags //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-8: rmi lam dri za'i grong khyer ltar //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-9: rab tu rnam par 'jig pa yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-10: rnam pa de lta'i 'dod pa rnams //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-11: khyad par 'jigs dang bcas pa yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-12: mi rtag sdug bsngal stong ba'i phyir //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-13: bdag gi blo ni mi bya'o //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-15: rab tu mi bzad bzod mi nus //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-16: nges par thams cad ltung ba yang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-17: mig med pas ni mthong ba'ang med //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-18: 'dod pa lnga ni thub mchog gis //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-19: stong pa'i ngo bor rab tu gsungs //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-20: 'dod chags khyim gyi rang bzhin ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-21: mi rtag pa dang sdug bsngal mang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-22: gzhan du min par rtogs ldan pas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-23: gang gang 'dod pa la mi chags //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-24: de ni pha rol 'gro rtag zhi //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-25: mya ngan 'das pa'i mtha' la gnas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-27: dbang po brlams par gyur pa'i sems //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-28: sdug bsngal brjod par sla min gang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-29: de la 'di na dpe yod min //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-30: ji lta ji ltar bde chen po //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:173b-31: sems ni sred pas nyer bcom pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-2: sdug bsngal chen po bzod par dka'//
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-3: legs byas las ni ma byas dang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-4: las kyi gnas lugs mi shes pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-5: sdug bsngal chen po kun 'byung bas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-6: phyis ni gdung bas sreg par byed //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-8: ji srid dal 'byor phun sum tshogs //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-9: de srid rang la phan par ma nos //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-12: 'chi ba mi yi sa rnams la //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-13: rig nas nye bar 'tshe bcas pa'i //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-14: srid na skyes bu su gnas byed //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-15: de ltar yang 'chi 'pho bar gyur pa'i lha rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-16: las kyi thag pas drangs par gyur pa so sor
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-17: nye bar bstan pas 'jigs pa chen po dang bcas
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-19: de'i phyir na lha de dag dud 'gro dang 'dra bar gyur pa yin te /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-20: gang dag yul rnams rnam par 'chums pa'i yid kyis
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-21: rang nyid la legs par mi byed do; ;de lta
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-22: bas na bag med par yang ma byed /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-23: phyi nas 'gyod par 'gyur bar ma byed cig /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-24: de ltar lha mu su lundhas tshogs pa rgyu ba
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-25: na rnam par rgyu ba'i lha rnams la rnam par
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-26: gzigs kyi mdzad pa'i mchod rten mthong bar byas nas
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-27: de la rjes su bsngags par byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174a-28: nges par legs pa la sbyor bar byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-0: 'dod pa rnams kyi @174b nyes dmigs rnams kyang rab tu ston par byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-1: rnam par smad par bya ba'i phyin ci log bzhi yang dag par ston par byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-2: 'chi ba'i dus ma 'ongs pa'ang legs par ston par byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-3: kun tu skrag par byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-4: de'i phyir 'jigs su rung ba'i 'chi ba las sdug
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-5: bsngal chus tshang ching du gyur pa'i lam lha de
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-6: dag rnams la bstan par gyur pa na /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-7: des rab tu dad pas yid 'phrog par byed pa'i
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-8: bde ba skyed par byed pa'i phyir na lha rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-11: rnam par gzigs kyis mdzad pa'i mdo sde gnyis pa rdzogs so ////
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-12: 'phags pa dam pa'i chos dran pa nye bar gzhag pa /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-13: bam po bzhi bcu rtsa dgu pa /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-14: gzhan yang mu su lundha de nyid kyis lha de
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-15: dag rnams nyid khrid de tshogs pa rgyu ba'i sa
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-16: la gnas pa'i gang dag sems bsgoms par gyur pa
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-17: dang / gang yang yid bsgoms par gyur pa dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-18: rgyud bsgoms par gyur pa de dag rnams khrid nas gzhan la phan par byed pa dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-19: gzhan la phan pa sbyor ba la brtson pas lha
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-20: de dag rnams kyi gzhan yang bag med ba de
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-21: dag gzhom par 'dod pas kyang las dang 'bras bu'i
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-22: de kho na nyid mthong ba dang dran par yang
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:174b-23: byas la / sems kyi rgyud dang bar yang byas shing /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-1: de dag rnams kyi rgyud shin tu rab kyi mchog
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-2: la sbyor bas 'dod pa rnams kyi nyes dmigs rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-3: kyang legs par bstan cing gson pa rnams kyang mi
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-4: rtag pa nyid kyi rtogs pa 'phangs shing 'khor ba'i
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-5: rgud pa rnams kyang brjod nas lha de dag rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-7: lha khyed rnams ltos dang mchod rten gsum pa gang de kho na mthong ba de ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-8: thub pa chen po gzhan 'khor ba 'jig dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-9: rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa; bla na med pa /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-10: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba ston pa'i yin te /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-11: rin po che rnams kyis legs par gang ba /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-12: 'od zer gyi phreng ba gser dang nor bu'i stegs
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-13: su nam mkha' 'bugs pa bzhin du shin tu mtho
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-14: bar gnas pa / skye bo thams cad rab tu dga' ba /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-15: 'thab bral gyi 'jig rten 'di dag thams cad zil gyis mnan nas nges par gnas pa /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-16: mchog tu zhi bar gyur pa dang mchog tu dga' bar gyur pa /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-17: sems kyi rgyud rlan pa bzhin du lha rnams thams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-18: cad kyi lha'i 'jig rten 'di'i rgyal mtshan du gyur
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175a-20: bsam gtan dang ldan pa bzhin du rnam par gnas so //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-0: rin po che shin tu 'bar @175b ba; rin po che'i 'od lham me bar gyur pa /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-1: dam pa'i chos ston par mdzad pa bzhin du mchog tu rgya che ba /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-2: dga' bar gyur par mthong ba 'di la bdag cag gis khrus gsol bar bya'o //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-3: bdag cag gis mchod par bya'o //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-4: tsandan yang bdag gis dbul bar bya'o //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-5: me tog dang spos la sogs pa rnams kyis mchod nas rim gyis bdag gis blta bar bya'o //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-6: ci 'dir drang srong chen por gyur pa de shin
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-7: tu ngo mtshar bar gyur pa 'dis ci zhig nye
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-9: gang gis bdag cag rnams nges par legs pa dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-13: rgyu gang gi phyir sems can rnams thams cad la phan par mi 'gyur ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-14: bde bar mi 'gyur ba'i bcom ldan 'das kyi mdzad pa ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-15: gang cung zad kyang mi mnga' ba'i phyir te /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-16: bdag nyid la phan pa'i don nyid kyis ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-17: 'di dag tu byon pa'ang ma yin no; ;de nas
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-18: lha de dag rnams kyis lha'i bdag po de'i tshig
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-19: nye bar bzung nas dge bar byas pa'i yid kyis
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-21: mchod pa'i don du bdag cag rnams mchi bar bgyi
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-22: zhing bdag nyid rjes su gzung ba'i don du dang;
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:175b-23: bdag nyid la phan pa'i don du bdag rnams 'gro
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-0: bar bya'o // de nas tshogs pa rgyu ba'i sa na gnas pa'i lha @176a *//
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-1: de dag rnams kyis lha'i bdag po mu su lundha
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-2: sngon du byas nas gang na bcom ldan 'das drang
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-3: srong gi mchog de'i mchod rten yod pa der nye
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-5: song nas kyang bcom ldan 'das 'khor ba 'jig gi
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-6: mchod rten la gus pa dang bcas pa'i yid kyis
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-8: g-yas phyogs nas bskor bar yang byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-9: de nas de'i tshe mchod rten gyi nang na rin
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-10: po che'i 'od shin tu 'bar ba rin po che
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:176a-11: de dag rnams gang gi khyad par gyis ni /

K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211a-18: mi rnams su gyur pa'i mi'i 'jig rten pa rnams kyi phun sum tshogs pa yin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211a-19: yang gzhan gang dag gi tshe na rgyu gzhan dag
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211a-20: dang rkyen gzhan rnams kyis lus de nyid la'ang reg
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211a-21: bya de nyid kyang mi 'dod par 'gyur te /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211a-22: yul gzhan rnams kyi dbang gis kyang mi 'dod par 'gyur ro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211a-23: gzhan yang yul rnams dang dbang po dang phrad pa
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211a-24: las skyes pa de'i rnam par rtog pa brtan pos
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211a-25: byas pa lan gcig ma yin zhing phyogs gcig ma
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-0: yin par rab tu 'phel bar gyur @211b pas sred
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-1: pa'i mes bsregs par gyur pa rnams gang yin pa
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-2: ni / rang bzhin gyis 'jig rten pa rnams thams cad chags pa yin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-3: ji lta bu'i bde ba rnams dang ldan pa'i 'jig
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-4: rten yul rnams la sred pas chags pa'i blo can
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-5: de dag rnams kyi rgud pa dang rjes su 'brel
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-6: ba'i dran pas rnam par dpyod par byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-7: mchog tu dge bar gyur pa'i dge slong des 'dod
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-8: pa na spyod pa'i lha drug po rnams kyi rgud
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-10: de la rgyal chen bzhi'i rigs kyi lha rnams la ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-11: rgud pa rnam pa bcu gnyis yin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-13: lha dang lha ma yin rnams kyis 'thab mo'i dus
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-14: na bang nyams pa dang lha ma yin gyis brgyab
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-15: pas lhan cig kho nar 'gyel ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-17: go cha rnams lhung ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-18: chags pa rnams dang lhan cig kho nar 'bye ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-19: chags shing ngo tsha ba rnams dang lhan cig tu mgo rgyan lhung bo dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-20: sgra gcan mthong bas brgyal pa dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-21: 'chi 'pho ba'i dus na tshad dang dbyibs dang rgyan
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-22: rnams dang ldan pa'i lha'i bu mo de dag rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-23: phyir gsar du skyes pa'i drung du song nas rtsed
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-24: mo chen po rtsed mo tshad med pa byed par
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:211b-25: gyur nas yongs su spangs pa dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-0: rtsed mo'i dus na de rang gi las dang mthun @212a *//
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-2: rtsed mo'i dus na dud 'gror skyes pa'i las byas kyang smad par byed pa dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-3: padma rnams la bsdad pa dang reg pa kho nas
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-4: nyams te rang gi las dang mthun par 'gyur ba
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-5: dang / rgyan rnams dang gzhan ches gtso bor gyur
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-6: pa dag gi rgyan rnams mngon par mthong nas ngo
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-8: rgud pa rnam pa bcu gnyis po de dag ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-9: rgyal chen bzhi'i ris kyi lha rnams kyi yin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-10: dge legs su rjes su spyod pa'i dge slong 'dis
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-11: mtho ris kyi bde ba la ma 'chums pa dri
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-12: ma med pa'i blos de dag rnams la kun nas
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-14: des mthong nas kyang gshi zhing mtho ris kyi bde ba rnams la smod par yang byed do //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-15: gang dag mtho ris 'dod pas tshangs par spyod pa de dag rnams kyi tshangs par spyod pa ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-16: mi tshangs par spyod pa'i don du spyod pa yin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-17: de rnams la'ang la phya bar byed cing skyug bro bar lta'o //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-19: rang dbang med pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-20: gzhan yang dge slong de nyid sum cu rtsa gsum
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-21: pa'i lha rnams kyi rgud pa la kun tu lta
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-22: bar byed do // des sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-23: lha rnams kyi rgud pa brgyad po mthong ba 'di
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212a-24: bar byed do // lta ste / lha dang lha
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-0: ma yin rnams @212b kyi rtsod pas go cha rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-2: gang gi tshe rab brtan gyi gshul nas ltung ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-3: mi gtsang bas rjes su 'brel ba'i dus su 'jug ngos rnams mi mthong ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-4: mthong bas sems stobs 'tshor ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-5: zas dang rtsed mo dag la 'jug pa'i dus su
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-6: kha dog dang gzugs dang stobs kyi ngo bo rnams
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-7: gzhan pa dang / sgra dang reg bya dang ro
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-8: dang gzugs dang dri rnams la'ang mi mnyam par brgya
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-9: byin yongs su shes pa dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-10: 'chi 'pho ba'i dus na bud med rnams 'phos par 'gyur ba dang /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-11: rtsed mo'i ltad mo khang bu rnams kyi bang bul par gyur pa rnams so //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-12: rgud pa brgyad po 'di dag rnams ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-13: sum cu rtsa gsum pa rnams kyi yin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-14: 'thab bral ba rnams kyi rgud pa rnams ni; 'di lta ste /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-15: bud med rnams kyis shes par 'gyur bas zas kyi dus na ngo tsha bar 'gyur ro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-16: de'i las rnams nyung ba yin pa'i phyir na lha
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-17: 'di la lha gzhan rnams kyis g-yog gi bya ba
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-18: mi byed de / dper na lha gzhan la lha
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-19: gzhan dag rnams kyis spyod par byed cing rgyal por
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-21: mu su lundha'i chos ston pa'i dus na shin tu 'jigs par 'gyur ba ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-22: mthar thug pa'i rgud pa yin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:212b-23: las rnams dman pa yin pa'i phyir na 'od rnams 'joms par 'gyur te /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-1: las kyi mtha' la spyod pa rnams kyi 'od kyis 'di zil gyis gnon par 'gyur te /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-2: de 'joms pa'ang mi'i 'jig rten na nyi mas gza' dang skar ma dang rgyu skar rnams bzhin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-3: las dman pa yin pa'i phyir na stan la nye
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-4: bar 'dug pa'i rin po che rnams gzhan nyid du
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-6: gang gi tshe dge ba'i las kyi mtha' la spyad pa'i lha rnams 'dug par 'gyur na /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-7: de'i tshe lha de'i stan rnams dngul gyi rang bzhin du grub par gyur pa ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-8: las rnam pa sna tshogs pa'i phyir ro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-12: rgud pa drug po de dag rnams ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-14: dga' ldan pa rnams la ni /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-16: 'di ltar ngang pa'i sgra kun nas sgrog pa mnyan
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-17: par 'os pa'i dam pa'i chos sgrog pa nyan par
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-18: byed pa'i rgyus dga' ldan pa rnams kyis thos na
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-19: mi dga' ba med pa nam mkha' la 'gro ba'i
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-20: rgyal po ngang pas rang gi gzugs 'dod pa bzhin
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-21: du bsgyur bas rin po che bdun gyis shin tu
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-22: 'bar ba'i cha byad kyis gzugs dpe med pa 'dzin
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-23: pa'i gzugs kyis dpag tshad lnga stong du rang gi
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213a-24: lus rnam par bsrings pa'i 'od kha dog sna tshogs
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-0: @213b ba rnams kyis dga' ldan kun tu snang bar
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-1: byas par gyur cing mchog tu ngo mtshar bar gyur
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-2: pa'i skad kyis lha de dag rnams la nyi ma
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-3: re re bzhin du 'gro bar byed pas nam mkha'
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-4: la bgrod pa'i rgyal po ngang pa byang chub sems
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-5: dpa' des tshigs su bcad pa brjod pa ji ltar
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-6: / gang phyir bsod nams rnams mi zad //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-7: tshe yang myur bar 'gro ba yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-8: dga' ldan gyi ni dbang phyug gis //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-9: chos legs bsdu la 'bad par gyis //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-10: gang yang chos ni yongs btang nas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-11: rgyags pas mchog tu nyer bcom pa; ;bsod nams gsog pa ma yin te //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-12: de ni phyi nas gdung bar 'gyur //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-13: ji srid du ni rgas dang nad //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-15: de srid du ni bsod nams kyis; ;phyi nas 'gyod par gyur ta re //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-16: bsod nams kun nas ma bsdus dang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-17: bag med pas kyang nyer bcom pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-18: dmyal ba'i rgyu yi sdug bsngal la //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-19: bag med pa ni bzhad gad byed //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-20: gson pa'i don des ci zhig bya //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-21: longs spyod kyis ci gnyen gyis ci //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-22: dbang po tshang ba de rnyed nas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-23: gang zhig chos la rtag mi dga'//
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-24: chos ni legs par bsdu ba'i yid //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-25: nyi ma re re bzhin du bya //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-26: sdig pa rnams ni rnam spangs dang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-27: bzang po rnams dang phrad par bya //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:213b-28: ye shes mtshon cha rnon po yis //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-1: rgyun gdul dka' bcad par gyis //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-2: skyon gyi phung po gzhom bya zhing //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-3: skyon gyi lam ni bcad par gyis //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-4: shes dang tshul khrims dka' thub spel; ;'dod pa dang bral spro ba spangs //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-5: de nyid lam ni rnam ston po //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-6: zhi ba rtag tu bsten par bya //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-7: tshul khrims gang gis lha skye ba //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-8: thob pa'i 'bras la rmongs pa yis; ;bsod nams gsog par mi byed cing //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-9: srid pa'i mtha' ni zlog mi byed //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-10: ye shes rtsol la mngon dga' gang //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-11: tshul khrims rin po che yis brgyan //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-13: lha rnams lhar ni 'dod pa yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-14: gang zhig rtag tu chos la dga'//
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-15: lha rnams rtag tu de phyag 'tshal //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-16: gang yang de las phyin ci log /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-17: de dag thams cad nyams par 'gyur //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-18: chos kyi zab pa 'di rnyed nas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-19: pha rol mchog tu sgrol ba che //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-20: gang zhig legs par zam mi rgal //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-21: de ni srid pa las mi grol //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-22: nyon mongs shing ni ma lus pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-23: ye shes me yis mi sreg pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-24: ci'i don nyon mongs yul gyi ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-25: dra bas mi rnams bsdams phyir ro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-26: 'thug po'i rang bzhin mig sprin tshogs //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-27: rab tu ye shes mig sbyong zhing //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-28: de las sgrol ba rdzogs sangs rgyas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214a-29: gsung gi rang bzhin sman gyi zas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-0: dam @214b chos dmag gi dpon gyis ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-2: dge mnga' shin tu bsgrags pas te //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-3: de ni rab tu 'bad pas mnyan //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-4: phyin ci log ni rnam pa bzhi //

K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-8: srid dra mi bzad chu bo ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-9: rnam rtog brgya phrag rgal bar dka'//

K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-11: thub rnams zhi bar rgal ba yin //

K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-13: lha gang 'dod pa sten pa rnams //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-14: rtag par yang ni gnas lnga ru //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-15: de dag rnams la 'grol ba med //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-16: lan gcig min par thob nyams pa'i //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-17: kimpa ka dang dug dang mtshon //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-18: me dang mtshungs pa'i sdug bsngal rgyu //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-20: ji lta ji ltar bsten byas pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-21: de lta de ltar rab tu 'phel //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-22: ngoms med byed phyir de dag ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-23: sred me'i rgyu yi me bzhin no //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-24: sreg skyon 'jigs pas nges brgyal ba'i //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-25: lha gang bde ba 'dod pa rnams //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-27: 'dod pa mi dge rnam spangs kyi //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-28: skye bo rmongs pa chags gyur cing //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-29: 'ching ba'ang dam por bsdams nas ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-30: tsab phral can ni gzhan du 'gro //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:214b-31: 'dod pa glog gi yon tan bzhin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-2: gong nas gong du 'dod pa sten //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-3: de ni 'dod chags mes bsregs nas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-4: bsregs bzhin bsregs pa thob par 'gyur //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-5: lha gang 'dod pa sten byed rnams //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-6: de dag gang phyir shin tu rmongs //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-7: med par bya phyir 'jug byed pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-8: gang de bde nas bde ba yin //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-10: grol med bde ba ci la yod //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-11: de phyir 'dod pa bsten mi bya //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-12: 'dod dang sdug bsngal mnyam du byung //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-13: yul gyi chags pa sten pa rnams //

K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-15: thams cad du ni legs 'phel ba'i //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-16: ngoms med bde ba'ang ga la yod //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-17: de phyir yid byung 'jigs bcas pa'i //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-18: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal rgya mtsho las //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-19: 'dod pa'i sred pa mi bzad pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-20: yongs su spongs shig sdig can de //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-21: ri yi tshogs ni de dag gi /
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-22: dga' ba'i ljon shing rnam snang tshogs; ;de dag la yang yongs brten nas //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-24: shes pa'i bden pa bzhi po ni //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-25: de dag mkhas pas rab legs mthong //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-26: bsam pa med ldan skye dang rga ba'i 'jigs pa las //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-27: rab tu grol ba mchog tu zhi ba dang ldan pa //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215a-28: bsam pa med ldan gang yang rnam par rmongs pa'i blo //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215b-0: 'dod @215b pa la chags srid pa'i longs spyod dag gis bcings //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215b-1: de ni 'dod pa'i rang bzhin 'ching rnams las ma grol //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215b-2: skye dang rga ba'i 'jigs pa rnams las 'grol ba
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215b-3: min; ;gang gi sdug bsngal rgya che 'di ni rnam
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215b-4: bsam nas // srid pa'i rgya mtsho las ni skyo bar mi 'gyur ba //
K10D0287-3_H0289-3:215b-5: de ni 'dod pa'i dug gi mda' yi shugs kyis rmongs //
